snippet: A medical examiner, striking a major blow to the defense of Michael Jackson’s doctor, said Tuesday that it was unreasonable to believe Mr. Jackson could have given himself a fatal dose of the powerful anesthetic propofol.
lead_paragraph: A medical examiner, striking a major blow to the defense of Michael Jackson’s doctor, said Tuesday that it was unreasonable to believe Mr. Jackson could have given himself a fatal dose of the powerful anesthetic propofol.

headline.main: California: Coroner Disputes Doctor in Jackson Death
